  "id": "1974829022774055136",
  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-119fve5\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"n3bXjltr\">只有中国大陆的医院仍然维持这种内部规定，港台有部分医生会征求家长意见（澳门地区因缺少公开资料不列出）。以下资料参考软件P。</p><p data-pid=\"u57Rpqsp\">港台<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=757387646&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB%E9%87%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%AF&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">性别重置手术<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>需要家属（父母）签名吗</p><p data-pid=\"h-2sYADP\">在港台地区，性别重置手术（变性手术）是否需要家属（父母）签名或同意，具体规定因地区、医院以及当事人年龄而异。</p><p data-pid=\"XW97xeM8\">- 香港要求接受性别重置手术者需提交医疗证明，但未有明确法律要求成年人必须由家属签名。实际操作中，成年患者通常自己签署<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=757387646&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E7%9F%A5%E6%83%85%E5%90%8C%E6%84%8F%E4%B9%A6&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">知情同意书<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>，如为未成年人则需监护人（通常是父母）同意[1][2]。</p><p data-pid=\"IMWbt58O\">- 台湾成年人接受性别重置手术原则上不强制要求家属签名，主由本人签署手术同意书[3][4]。</p><p data-pid=\"XD5CeJoz\">- 某些医院出于医疗争议和法律风险考虑，会“建议”或“希望”家属（如父母）知情签字，尤其是18岁以下者则一定需要监护人同意[4][5]。</p><p data-pid=\"x4e9ZTxz\">- 若患者为未成年人，必须经过父母（或法定监护人）同意和签名。</p><p data-pid=\"TlddyLSn\">实际操作与争议</p><p data-pid=\"JiEgmJzZ\">- 成年人依法享有<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=757387646&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%8C%BB%E7%96%97%E8%87%AA%E4%B8%BB%E6%9D%83&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">医疗自主权<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>，港澳台多由个人签字。部分医院为避免后续纷争，可能建议家属一同知情签字，但法律上非强制[4].</p><p data-pid=\"17lfzVfz\">- 医疗团队会对<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=757387646&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">精神健康<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>、知情同意度进行评估，但成年人在满足精神科评估和诊断书等要求后通常不需家属强制参与[3].</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"szXhPxiM\">结论：港台地区，性别重置手术对成年人通常不强制要求家属（父母）签名，但未成年人则必须家属签名。部分医院为审慎也可能建议家属知情参与，但非法律硬性规定[3][4][5][1][2]。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"JF4FpUEY\">引用：</p><p data-pid=\"o1hxRKZ8\">[1] [PDF] 申請更改香港身份證上性別記項的指引 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.immd.gov.hk/pdf/the-guideline-tc.pdf\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://www.</span><span class=\"visible\">immd.gov.hk/pdf/the-gui</span><span class=\"invisible\">deline-tc.pdf</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></p><p data-pid=\"I-BZMaqg\">[2] 中國台灣：若完成改變性徵手術及符合條件可申請改變身份證上性別 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//news.tvb.com/tc/local/660ccf9a6a2523f7fda9b92c/%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25BE%25B3-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E8%258B%25A5%25E5%25AE%258C%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%2594%25B9%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%2580%25A7%25E5%25BE%25B5%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25A1%2593%25E6%2588%2596%25E7%25AC%25A6%25E5%2590%2588%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BB%25B6-%25E5%258F%25AF%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E6%2594%25B9%25E8%25AE%258A%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%2580%25A7%25E5%2588%25A5\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">news.tvb.com/tc/local/6</span><span class=\"invisible\">60ccf9a6a2523f7fda9b92c/%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%8B%A5%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E6%94%B9%E8%AE%8A%E6%80%A7%E5%BE%B5%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E6%88%96%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E6%A2%9D%E4%BB%B6-%E5%8F%AF%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E6%94%B9%E8%AE%8A%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E8%AD%89%E4%B8%8A%E6%80%A7%E5%88%A5</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></p><p data-pid=\"cFdUGzJ6\">[3] [PDF] 第三章認識跨性別者（T）及其處境 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.boca.gov.tw/dl-2331-7e983e47d7e043f3b9c6d19c66e9d68a.html\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://www.</span><span class=\"visible\">boca.gov.tw/dl-2331-7e9</span><span class=\"invisible\">83e47d7e043f3b9c6d19c66e9d68a.html</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></p><p data-pid=\"JFODURlc\">[4] 醫療現場關係人與代理人法規落實的阻礙與困境 - 台灣同志諮詢熱線 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//hotline.org.tw/blog/1015\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">hotline.org.tw/blog/101</span><span class=\"invisible\">5</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></p><p data-pid=\"yISPbZic\">[5] 做變性手術前為什麼要簽同意書？！醫師詳細說分明！ft.整形外科 ... <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/watch%3Fv%3Dxc18jiyjK3g\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://www.</span><span class=\"visible\">youtube.com/watch?</span><span class=\"invisible\">v=xc18jiyjK3g</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></p><p data-pid=\"WOPJC_Eg\">[6] 中国跨性别者悲歌:“家人决定我是谁” - DW <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.dw.com/zh/%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259B%25BD%25E8%25B7%25A8%25E6%2580%25A7%25E5%2588%25AB%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%2582%25B2%25E6%25AD%258C%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2586%25B3%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%2598%25AF%25E8%25B0%2581/a-48800958\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://www.</span><span class=\"visible\">dw.com/zh/%E4%B8%AD%E5%</span><span class=\"invisible\">9B%BD%E8%B7%A8%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB%E8%80%85%E6%82%B2%E6%AD%8C%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E6%88%91%E6%98%AF%E8%B0%81/a-48800958</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></p><p data-pid=\"6Z9vYNI-\">[7] 中华人民共和国LGBT权益- 维基百科，自由的百科全书 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//zh.wikipedia.org/zh-cn/%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258D%258E%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%259